거래 시간 분류¶

DAY: 12:00 ~ 14:59
MID: 15:00 ~ 16:59
EVENING: 17:00 ~ 20:00

In [27]:
def time_split(js_data):
    for i in range(0, len(js_data)):
        if (js_data.loc[i, ''].time()<time(15, 0)):
            js_data.loc[i, '']='DAY'
        elif (js_data.loc[i, ''].time()<time(17, 0)):
            js_data.loc[i, '']='MID'
        else:
            js_data.loc[i, '']='EVENING'

def drop_pay(js_data):
    js_cancel = js_data[js_data.=='CANCEL'][''].values.tolist()
    temp=js_data[js_data[''].isin(js_cancel)]
    idx = temp[temp.=='PAY'][''].index
    js_data.drop(idx, axis=0, inplace=True)

cnt=1
for i in pay_bread:
    if i.find('x')==-1:
        bread_df.loc[i,'PAY']=bread_df.loc[i,'PAY']+1
        bread_df.loc[i,'1']=bread_df.loc[i,'1']+1

        cnt=int(i[i.find('x')+1:])
        bread_df.loc[i[:i.find('x')], 'PAY']=bread_df.loc[i[:i.find('x')], 'PAY']+cnt
        if cnt>=3:
            bread_df.loc[i[:i.find('x')], '3'] = bread_df.loc[i[:i.find('x')], '3']+1
